      "_instructions": "Airport data is derived from BTS T-100 (run bts_collector first). HHI = sum of squared carrier seat shares at each airport. HHI > 2500 = concentrated (fortress hub), 1500-2500 = moderate, < 1500 = competitive. Supplement with FAA ATADS for operations data and ACI-NA for annual totals."
    }
  }
}